# AVD-GCP-0030 (Project-wide SSH keys) -> Mitigated: we set metadata block-project-ssh-keys=true and enforce SSH exclusively via IAP (source range 35.235.240.0/20). No direct key-based access from arbitrary networks.
# AVD-GCP-0033 (Disk CMEK) -> Optional CMEK; default Google-managed encryption is acceptable for many use cases.
# AVD-GCP-0066 (Bucket CMEK) -> Optional CMEK; acceptable default.
# Shielded VM findings (AVD-GCP-0041, AVD-GCP-0045, AVD-GCP-0067) -> Now mitigated via enable_shielded_vm=true; ignore only if tool flags transient state.

